    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "EFFECTIVE APRIL 28, 1957\nCOMPLETE SYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEASTERN\nAIR LINES\n* ANNIVERSARY\nIMPORTANT: PLEASE RE-CONFIRM\nYOUR RESERVATION\nSEE PAGE 23\nSAVE 10% ON RETURN PORTION\nOF STANDARD ROUND TRIP TICKET\nALWAYS BUY ROUND TRIP",
      "FLY-EASTERN AIR LINES\nMAY—1957\nSun Mon Tue Wed Thu\n2\nJUNE—1957\nSun Mon Tue Wed Thu Fri\n5\n12\n19\n26\n6\n7\n8\n13\n14\n15\n20 21\n22\n27 28\n29\nFri\nSat\n3\n10\n16\n17\n18\n23\n24 25\n30\n31\nSat\n2\n9\n16\n3\n4 5\n6\n7\n8\n10\n12\n13 14\n15\n17\n18\n19\n20 21\n22\n24\n25\n26 27 28 29\nBring the Family along\non EASTERN'S\n½ FARE\nFAMILY PLAN\nPurchase of one full-fare Eastern Air\nLines ticket by one parent entitles\nother parent and all children ages 2\nthrough 21 to ride ½-Fare on any\nTuesday,\nWednesday or Thursday.\nNo round trip discount except for\nchildren, ages 2 through 11. This\nplan does not apply on Aircoaches.\nOn all flights, every day of the week, one child under 2 carried FREE...\nchildren 2 and over, but under 12, travel ½ fare."
    ],
